Customizing GNOME with Just Perfection ExtensionAdd new customization aspects to your Linux desktop with Just Perfection GNOME Extension. https://itsfoss.com/just-perfection-gnome-extension/ 64e2f4c72378340cb823babf Customization ⚙️Sagar Sharma Wed, 20 Sep 2023 07:22:13 GMT <img src="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/09/customising-gnome-with-just-perfection.png" alt="Customizing GNOME with Just Perfection Extension"><p> GNOME 是 Linux 世界中<a href="https://itsfoss.com/best-linux-desktop-environments/" rel="noreferrer">最流行的桌面环境之一</a>。</p><p>但如果我们讨论 GNOME 的可定制性方面，那么您就不会像 KDE 那样获得很多选择。</p><p>并不是说您不能<a href="https://itsfoss.com/gnome-tricks-ubuntu/">自定义 GNOME</a> 。 GUI 工具<a href="https://itsfoss.com/gnome-tweak-tool/">GNOME Tweaks</a>可帮助您进行一些简单的配置更改。对于高级设置更改，您必须依赖<a href="https://wiki.gnome.org/Apps/DconfEditor?ref=itsfoss.com">dconf 编辑器</a>，这对许多人来说可能是令人生畏的。</p><p>在定制方面，让我向您介绍<strong>Just Perfection</strong> GNOME 扩展，它可以让您同时调整桌面的各个方面。</p><h2 id="just-perfection-the-do-it-all-extension-%F0%9F%8C%9F">完美，全能扩展🌟 </h2><figure class="kg-card kg-image-card"><img src="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/just-perfection-extension-in-GNOME.png" class="kg-image" alt="使用 Just Perfect 扩展自定义 GNOME" loading="lazy" width="1070" height="662" srcset="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w600/2023/08/just-perfection-extension-in-GNOME.png 600w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w1000/2023/08/just-perfection-extension-in-GNOME.png 1000w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/just-perfection-extension-in-GNOME.png 1070w" sizes="(min-width: 720px) 720px"></figure><p>如果 Just Perfection 扩展被命名为<code>Do it all</code>会更有意义。当我向您介绍它的功能集时，我会更加清楚。</p><p>使用此扩展，您将能够调整一些小事情，例如您希望如何处理 Dock、通知面板、图标以及与 GNOME 的交互。</p><p>以下是 Just Perfection 工具的一些主要功能：</p><ul><li> 4 个预配置配置文件</li><li>能够启用/禁用超级键、动画、面板、时钟、日历等。</li><li>能够启用/禁用应用程序菜单、面板通知、电源图标和活动的图标。</li><li>自定义面板、通知栏、OSD 位置（音量/亮度弹出窗口）、窗口大小以及按下<code>Alt + tab</code>时的应用程序预览。</li><li>更改工作区预览的行为、是否显示工作区切换器、打开应用程序网格的方式等等。</li></ul><p>听起来太有希望了。正确的？</p><h3 id="how-to-install-just-perfection">如何安装完美</h3><p><a href="https://itsfoss.com/gnome-shell-extensions/" rel="noreferrer">在 Linux 中安装 GNOME 扩展有多种方法</a>。其中之一是通过网络浏览器安装。</p><p>要使用网络浏览器安装它，请访问他们的官方下载页面：</p><div class="kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center"> <a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/3843/just-perfection/?ref=itsfoss.com" class="kg-btn kg-btn-accent">追求完美</a></div><p>安装完成后，您将在下载页面上看到设置图标，单击该按钮，它将打开一个提示来调整 Just Perfection 扩展： </p><figure class="kg-card kg-image-card"><img src="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/how-to-use-gnome-extensions-after-installing-them.png" class="kg-image" alt="使用 Just Perfect 扩展自定义 GNOME" loading="lazy" width="1467" height="1039" srcset="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w600/2023/08/how-to-use-gnome-extensions-after-installing-them.png 600w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w1000/2023/08/how-to-use-gnome-extensions-after-installing-them.png 1000w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/how-to-use-gnome-extensions-after-installing-them.png 1467w" sizes="(min-width: 720px) 720px"></figure><figure class="kg-card kg-bookmark-card kg-card-hascaption"> <a class="kg-bookmark-container" href="https://itsfoss.click/protonmail?ref=itsfoss.com"><div class="kg-bookmark-content"><div class="kg-bookmark-title">Proton Mail：获取私人、安全且加密的电子邮件帐户 | Proton</div> <div class="kg-bookmark-description">Proton Mail 是全球最大的安全电子邮件服务，拥有超过 1 亿用户。可在 Web、iOS、Android 和桌面上使用。受瑞士隐私法保护。</div> <div class="kg-bookmark-metadata"><img class="kg-bookmark-icon" src="https://itsfoss.click/favicons/apple-touch-icon.png" alt="使用 Just Perfect 扩展自定义 GNOME"><span class="kg-bookmark-author">质子</span></div></div><div class="kg-bookmark-thumbnail"><img src="https://proton.me/images/social/proton-mail-og.png" alt="使用 Just Perfect 扩展自定义 GNOME"></div></a><figcaption><p dir="ltr"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">合作伙伴链接</span></p></figcaption></figure><h2 id="how-to-use-the-just-perfection-gnome-extension">如何使用 Just Perfection GNOME 扩展</h2><p>使用此扩展的最方便方法是在 4 个预配置配置文件之间进行选择。</p><p>可选，但我建议启用覆盖 shell 主题的选项，以使您的桌面在视觉上更具吸引力： </p><figure class="kg-card kg-image-card"><img src="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/override-shell-theme-in-just-perfection-extension.png" class="kg-image" alt="使用 Just Perfect 扩展自定义 GNOME" loading="lazy" width="963" height="598" srcset="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w600/2023/08/override-shell-theme-in-just-perfection-extension.png 600w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/override-shell-theme-in-just-perfection-extension.png 963w" sizes="(min-width: 720px) 720px"></figure><p>执行此操作后，它将自动切换到<code>Custom</code>配置文件并使扩展坞背景透明。</p><p>各简介简介：</p><ul><li> <code>Default</code> ：默认配置文件不会应用任何更改，但如果启用 shell 覆盖，它会稍微减小面板和停靠的大小。</li><li> <code>Custom</code> ：当您启用 shell 覆盖并使扩展坞背景透明时被激活。</li><li> <code>Minimal</code> ：减小扩展坞和面板的尺寸，以拥有更多的屏幕区域可供使用。</li><li> <code>Super Minimal</code> ：移除底座和面板，以获得干净的外观和最大的屏幕区域。</li></ul><p>以下是在这些配置文件之间切换时的预期行为： </p><figure class="kg-card kg-video-card kg-width-regular" data-kg-thumbnail="https://itsfoss.com/content/media/2023/08/how-to-use-the-pre-configured-profiles-in-the-just-perfection-GNOME-extension_thumb.jpg" data-kg-custom-thumbnail><div class="kg-video-container"><video src="https://itsfoss.com/content/media/2023/08/how-to-use-the-pre-configured-profiles-in-the-just-perfection-GNOME-extension.webm" poster="https://img.spacergif.org/v1/1920x1080/0a/spacer.png" width="1920" height="1080" loop autoplay muted playsinline preload="metadata" style="background: transparent url(&apos;https://itsfoss.com/content/media/2023/08/how-to-use-the-pre-configured-profiles-in-the-just-perfection-GNOME-extension_thumb.jpg&apos;) 50% 50% / cover no-repeat;"></video><div class="kg-video-overlay"><path d="M23.14 10.608 2.253.164A1.559 1.559 0 0 0 0 1.557v20.887a1.558 1.558 0 0 0 2.253 1.392L23.14 13.393a1.557 1.557 0 0 0 0-2.785Z"/></div><div class="kg-video-player-container kg-video-hide"><div class="kg-video-player"><path d="M23.14 10.608 2.253.164A1.559 1.559 0 0 0 0 1.557v20.887a1.558 1.558 0 0 0 2.253 1.392L23.14 13.393a1.557 1.557 0 0 0 0-2.785Z"/><rect x="3" y="1" width="7" height="22" rx="1.5" ry="1.5"/><rect x="14" y="1" width="7" height="22" rx="1.5" ry="1.5"/> <span class="kg-video-current-time">0:00</span><div class="kg-video-time"> / <span class="kg-video-duration">0:08</span></div><input type="range" class="kg-video-seek-slider" max="100" value="0"> <button class="kg-video-playback-rate">1×</button> <path d="M15.189 2.021a9.728 9.728 0 0 0-7.924 4.85.249.249 0 0 1-.221.133H5.25a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v2a3 3 0 0 0 3 3h1.794a.249.249 0 0 1 .221.133 9.73 9.73 0 0 0 7.924 4.85h.06a1 1 0 0 0 1-1V3.02a1 1 0 0 0-1.06-.998Z"/><path d="M16.177 4.3a.248.248 0 0 0 .073-.176v-1.1a1 1 0 0 0-1.061-1 9.728 9.728 0 0 0-7.924 4.85.249.249 0 0 1-.221.133H5.25a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v2a3 3 0 0 0 3 3h.114a.251.251 0 0 0 .177-.073ZM23.707 1.706A1 1 0 0 0 22.293.292l-22 22a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.414l.009.009a1 1 0 0 0 1.405-.009l6.63-6.631A.251.251 0 0 1 8.515 17a.245.245 0 0 1 .177.075 10.081 10.081 0 0 0 6.5 2.92 1 1 0 0 0 1.061-1V9.266a.247.247 0 0 1 .073-.176Z"/><input type="range" class="kg-video-volume-slider" max="100" value="100"></div></div></div></figure><p>现在，您可以启用/禁用不同的选项来获得您喜欢的桌面。</p><h2 id="going-minimal-with-just-perfection">追求简约，追求完美</h2><p>在本节中，我将向您展示如何获得受 Linux Mint 的 Cinnamon 桌面启发的最小桌面体验，如下所示： </p><figure class="kg-card kg-image-card"><img src="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/main-desktop-with-message.png" class="kg-image" alt="使用 Just Perfect 扩展自定义 GNOME" loading="lazy" width="1942" height="1097" srcset="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w600/2023/08/main-desktop-with-message.png 600w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w1000/2023/08/main-desktop-with-message.png 1000w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w1600/2023/08/main-desktop-with-message.png 1600w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/main-desktop-with-message.png 1942w" sizes="(min-width: 720px) 720px"></figure><p>这是切换工作空间时的样子： </p><figure class="kg-card kg-image-card"><img src="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/activities-after-customisation.png" class="kg-image" alt="使用 Just Perfect 扩展自定义 GNOME" loading="lazy" width="1942" height="1073" srcset="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w600/2023/08/activities-after-customisation.png 600w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w1000/2023/08/activities-after-customisation.png 1000w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w1600/2023/08/activities-after-customisation.png 1600w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/activities-after-customisation.png 1942w" sizes="(min-width: 720px) 720px"></figure><p>这是我为使我的桌面看起来最小化而所做的，如上所示：</p><ul><li>透明底座位于右侧（从系统菜单）</li><li>将面板位置更改为底部</li><li>从面板中删除<code>Application menu</code>和<code>Activities</code></li><li>将时钟重新定位到左下角</li><li>将通知弹出窗口放置在左下角</li><li>启用工作区切换器</li><li>增加工作区概览窗格的半径</li></ul><p>当然，您可以跳过所示的任何步骤。</p><h3 id="1-transparent-dock-positioned-to-the-right"> 1. 透明底座位于右侧</h3><p>要拥有透明底座，您所要做的就是从<code>Profile</code>文件”菜单中选择<code>Custom</code> ”并启用<code>Shell Theme</code>选项： </p><figure class="kg-card kg-image-card"><img src="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/Use-custom-profile-in-just-perfection-GNOME-extension.png" class="kg-image" alt="使用 Just Perfect 扩展自定义 GNOME" loading="lazy" width="1087" height="592" srcset="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w600/2023/08/Use-custom-profile-in-just-perfection-GNOME-extension.png 600w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w1000/2023/08/Use-custom-profile-in-just-perfection-GNOME-extension.png 1000w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/Use-custom-profile-in-just-perfection-GNOME-extension.png 1087w" sizes="(min-width: 720px) 720px"></figure><p>如果您使用的是 Ubuntu 的最新版本，那么您将在系统菜单中找到重新定位扩展坞的选项。</p><p>首先，从系统菜单打开设置，然后打开<code>Appearance</code>菜单。在<strong>“Dock”</strong>部分中，您将找到<code>Position on screen</code>选项。</p><p>在那里，选择<code>Right</code> ： </p><figure class="kg-card kg-image-card"><img src="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/change-position-of-dock-1.png" class="kg-image" alt="使用 Just Perfect 扩展自定义 GNOME" loading="lazy" width="1002" height="466" srcset="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w600/2023/08/change-position-of-dock-1.png 600w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w1000/2023/08/change-position-of-dock-1.png 1000w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/change-position-of-dock-1.png 1002w" sizes="(min-width: 720px) 720px"></figure><p>如果您使用的是旧版本的 GNOME，那么您将找不到此菜单。</p><p>但不用担心，您可以通过<a href="https://news.itsfoss.com/dash-to-dock-gnome-40/?ref=itsfoss.com" rel="noreferrer">安装名为 Dash to Dock 的扩展来获得同样的好处。</a></p><p>在这里，您必须更改两个设置：</p><ul><li>将屏幕上的位置更改为<code>Right</code></li><li>取消选中面板模式（如果选中） </li></ul><figure class="kg-card kg-image-card"><img src="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/Change-dock-position-using-the-dask-to-dock-extension.png" class="kg-image" alt="使用 Just Perfect 扩展自定义 GNOME" loading="lazy" width="1118" height="882" srcset="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w600/2023/08/Change-dock-position-using-the-dask-to-dock-extension.png 600w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w1000/2023/08/Change-dock-position-using-the-dask-to-dock-extension.png 1000w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/Change-dock-position-using-the-dask-to-dock-extension.png 1118w" sizes="(min-width: 720px) 720px"></figure><h3 id="2-relocate-the-panel-to-the-bottom"> 2. 将面板移至底部</h3><p>要将面板重新定位到底部，请转到<code>Customize</code>菜单，您将在其中找到<code>Panel Position</code>选项。</p><p>双击该选项并选择<code>Bottom</code> ： </p><figure class="kg-card kg-image-card"><img src="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/change-panel-to-bottom-in-GNOME.png" class="kg-image" alt="使用 Just Perfect 扩展自定义 GNOME" loading="lazy" width="1027" height="752" srcset="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w600/2023/08/change-panel-to-bottom-in-GNOME.png 600w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w1000/2023/08/change-panel-to-bottom-in-GNOME.png 1000w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/change-panel-to-bottom-in-GNOME.png 1027w" sizes="(min-width: 720px) 720px"></figure><h3 id="3-change-the-clock-position-to-the-left-corner"> 3.将时钟位置更改为左角</h3><p>在过去的 6 个月里，我一直以这种方式使用时钟，它为我的工作流程创造了奇迹。简单来说，您更频繁地看时钟，这样您就可以更快地应对时间。</p><p>看起来也不错！</p><p>要更改时钟的位置，请转到<code>Customize</code>菜单，然后找到<code>Clock Menu Position</code>选项并选择“ <code>Left</code>选项： </p><figure class="kg-card kg-image-card"><img src="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/change-clock-position-to-left.png" class="kg-image" alt="使用 Just Perfect 扩展自定义 GNOME" loading="lazy" width="1087" height="592" srcset="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w600/2023/08/change-clock-position-to-left.png 600w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w1000/2023/08/change-clock-position-to-left.png 1000w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/change-clock-position-to-left.png 1087w" sizes="(min-width: 720px) 720px"></figure><h3 id="4-remove-the-application-menu-and-activities-button"> 4.删除应用程序菜单和活动按钮</h3><figure class="kg-card kg-image-card"><img src="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/Remove-Activities-and-App-menu-from-Ubuntu-GNOME.png" class="kg-image" alt="使用 Just Perfect 扩展自定义 GNOME" loading="lazy" width="1338" height="266" srcset="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w600/2023/08/Remove-Activities-and-App-menu-from-Ubuntu-GNOME.png 600w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w1000/2023/08/Remove-Activities-and-App-menu-from-Ubuntu-GNOME.png 1000w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/Remove-Activities-and-App-menu-from-Ubuntu-GNOME.png 1338w" sizes="(min-width: 720px) 720px"></figure><p>还没有看到很多用户使用这两个选项，那么为什么不简单地删除它们并实现干净的最小外观呢？</p><p>为此，请转到<code>Visibility</code>菜单并禁用以下两个选项：</p><ul><li>活动按钮</li><li>应用程序菜单</li></ul><figure class="kg-card kg-image-card"><img src="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/disable-Activities-and-App-menu-from-Ubuntu-GNOME.png" class="kg-image" alt="使用 Just Perfect 扩展自定义 GNOME" loading="lazy" width="1075" height="501" srcset="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w600/2023/08/disable-Activities-and-App-menu-from-Ubuntu-GNOME.png 600w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w1000/2023/08/disable-Activities-and-App-menu-from-Ubuntu-GNOME.png 1000w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/disable-Activities-and-App-menu-from-Ubuntu-GNOME.png 1075w" sizes="(min-width: 720px) 720px"></figure><h3 id="5-notification-pop-up-re-positioned-to-bottom-right"> 5.通知弹出窗口重新定位到右下角</h3><p>由于面板本身被重新定位到底部，因此在顶部弹出窗口没有任何意义（至少对我来说）。此外，与顶部相比，从底部读取消息更容易。</p><p>为此，请遵循以下两个简单步骤：</p><ul><li>转到<code>Customize</code>菜单</li><li>从<code>Notification Banner Position</code>选择<code>Bottom End</code> ： </li></ul><figure class="kg-card kg-image-card"><img src="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/change-notification-pop-up-location-in-GNOME.png" class="kg-image" alt="使用 Just Perfect 扩展自定义 GNOME" loading="lazy" width="1087" height="480" srcset="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w600/2023/08/change-notification-pop-up-location-in-GNOME.png 600w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w1000/2023/08/change-notification-pop-up-location-in-GNOME.png 1000w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/change-notification-pop-up-location-in-GNOME.png 1087w" sizes="(min-width: 720px) 720px"></figure><h3 id="6-enable-workspace-switcher"> 6. 启用工作区切换器</h3><p>在概览多个工作区的活动时，工作区切换器会显示每个工作区的预览。</p><p>还困惑吗？启用后看起来像这样： </p><figure class="kg-card kg-image-card"><img src="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/enable-workspace-switcher-in-GNOME-overview.png" class="kg-image" alt="使用 Just Perfect 扩展自定义 GNOME" loading="lazy" width="1942" height="1073" srcset="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w600/2023/08/enable-workspace-switcher-in-GNOME-overview.png 600w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w1000/2023/08/enable-workspace-switcher-in-GNOME-overview.png 1000w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w1600/2023/08/enable-workspace-switcher-in-GNOME-overview.png 1600w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/enable-workspace-switcher-in-GNOME-overview.png 1942w" sizes="(min-width: 720px) 720px"></figure><p>使用此功能，您只需按超级键即可清楚地了解每个工作区中发生的情况。</p><p>当然，您可以通过打开系统菜单（按两次超级键）来获得相同的视图，但是当它可以在概述本身中启用时，为什么要浪费一次按键并打开系统菜单呢？</p><p>要启用此功能，您必须遵循三个简单的步骤：</p><ul><li>转到<code>Behavior</code>菜单并启用<code>Always Show Workspace Switcher</code></li><li>转到<code>Customize</code>菜单</li><li>为<code>Workspace Switcher Size</code>选择<code>11%</code> </li></ul><figure class="kg-card kg-image-card"><img src="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/enable-always-show-workspace-switcher.png" class="kg-image" alt="使用 Just Perfect 扩展自定义 GNOME" loading="lazy" width="1699" height="860" srcset="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w600/2023/08/enable-always-show-workspace-switcher.png 600w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w1000/2023/08/enable-always-show-workspace-switcher.png 1000w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w1600/2023/08/enable-always-show-workspace-switcher.png 1600w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/enable-always-show-workspace-switcher.png 1699w" sizes="(min-width: 720px) 720px"></figure><p>我增加工作区切换器大小的原因是默认视图非常小。</p><h3 id="7-increase-the-radius-of-the-workspace-overview-pane"> 7.增加工作区概览窗格的半径</h3><p>我喜欢圆角，尤其是在工作区概览窗格上应用圆角时，特别是当壁纸与设置相得益彰时。</p><p>以下是应用所示设置后的外观： </p><figure class="kg-card kg-image-card"><img src="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/Change-corner-radius-of-workspace-switcher-pane-in-GNOME-ubuntu.png" class="kg-image" alt="使用 Just Perfect 扩展自定义 GNOME" loading="lazy" width="1942" height="1073" srcset="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w600/2023/08/Change-corner-radius-of-workspace-switcher-pane-in-GNOME-ubuntu.png 600w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w1000/2023/08/Change-corner-radius-of-workspace-switcher-pane-in-GNOME-ubuntu.png 1000w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w1600/2023/08/Change-corner-radius-of-workspace-switcher-pane-in-GNOME-ubuntu.png 1600w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/Change-corner-radius-of-workspace-switcher-pane-in-GNOME-ubuntu.png 1942w" sizes="(min-width: 720px) 720px"></figure><p>使用以下步骤增加工作区概览面板的半径</p><ul><li>转到<code>Customize</code>菜单</li><li>在<code>Workspace Background Corner Size</code>中选择<code>60px</code> （最大量） </li></ul><figure class="kg-card kg-image-card"><img src="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/increse-radius-of-workspace-corners-in-GNOME-Ubuntu.png" class="kg-image" alt="使用 Just Perfect 扩展自定义 GNOME" loading="lazy" width="1076" height="479" srcset="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w600/2023/08/increse-radius-of-workspace-corners-in-GNOME-Ubuntu.png 600w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w1000/2023/08/increse-radius-of-workspace-corners-in-GNOME-Ubuntu.png 1000w, https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/08/increse-radius-of-workspace-corners-in-GNOME-Ubuntu.png 1076w" sizes="(min-width: 720px) 720px"></figure><h2 id="more-on-gnome-customization">有关 GNOME 定制的更多信息</h2><p>如果您是 Ubuntu 新手，那么我们有一份详细的指南，将引导您了解<a href="https://itsfoss.com/gnome-tricks-ubuntu/" rel="noreferrer">如何自定义 GNOME</a>的所有基础知识：</p><figure class="kg-card kg-bookmark-card"> <a class="kg-bookmark-container" href="https://itsfoss.com/gnome-tricks-ubuntu/"><div class="kg-bookmark-content"><div class="kg-bookmark-title">自定义 Ubuntu GNOME 的 15 个简单技巧</div><div class="kg-bookmark-description">一些基本且有趣的 GNOME 自定义技巧，可丰富您的体验并充分利用您的 Ubuntu 桌面。</div> <div class="kg-bookmark-metadata"><img class="kg-bookmark-icon" src="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/size/w256h256/2022/12/android-chrome-192x192.png" alt="使用 Just Perfect 扩展自定义 GNOME"><span class="kg-bookmark-author">这是 FOSS</span> <span class="kg-bookmark-publisher">Abhishek Prakash</span></div></div> <div class="kg-bookmark-thumbnail"><img src="https://itsfoss.com/content/images/2023/03/gnome-customisation-tips.png" alt="使用 Just Perfect 扩展自定义 GNOME"></div></a></figure><p>以下是如何使用 GNOME 调整工具让 GNOME 变得更加出色：</p><figure class="kg-card kg-bookmark-card"> <a class="kg-bookmark-container" href="https://itsfoss.com/gnome-tweak-tool/"><div class="kg-bookmark-content"><div class="kg-bookmark-title">